sp.l:
Took it! 'Sheartlikins we'll have the great one too;
'tis ours by Conquest.—prithee help me up and I'll pull it
down—

You know I was never guilty of that Folly, my dear Phillippo;
but with your self—but come, let's see what we have got
by this.

Charitable Sir, you've told your self already what I am;
a very wretched Maid, forc't by a strange unlucky accident, to
seek a safety here,
